data.description: Literally, minutes from The Strip and only 0.8 miles away from the world-famous Palms Casino Resort.  The location is everything! Close to shopping, entertainment, restaurants, and the freeway in the private gated Flamingo Heights community. This 1st floor condo is cozy, well well-designed with an open floor plan and generous room sizes.  The large Living room features a gas fireplace leading to the dining area with access to the covered patio. This home is a must-see.
